3
00:00:09,890 --> 00:00:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh, so guys like that are your type, eh?</font>

4
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

5
00:00:15,610 --> 00:00:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

6
00:00:18,860 --> 00:00:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the <i>song</i> I like.</font>

7
00:00:20,490 --> 00:00:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

8
00:00:22,510 --> 00:00:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel you.</font>

9
00:00:24,110 --> 00:00:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do parents say stuff like that?</font>

10
00:00:26,430 --> 00:00:29,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like we're fantasizing 
about dating them.</font>

11
00:00:29,240 --> 00:00:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

12
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know how I'm more 
into girls? Like idols?</font>

13
00:00:33,270 --> 00:00:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, my parents think 
I want to become one.</font>

14
00:00:37,010 --> 00:00:38,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way!</font>

15
00:00:38,530 --> 00:00:40,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They totally don't get it.</font>

16
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're full of contradictions.</font>

17
00:00:42,260 --> 00:00:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our parents and teachers, I mean.</font>

18
00:00:43,870 --> 00:00:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

19
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa.</font>

20
00:00:46,210 --> 00:00:48,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do whatever you want.</font>

21
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:51,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be whoever you want to be.</font>

22
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope I don't become an adult like that.</font>

23
00:00:54,210 --> 00:00:55,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For sure!</font>

24
00:00:55,750 --> 00:00:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll always be on your side.</font>

25
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, Asa?</font>

26
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:12,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah, could you pick up some 
toilet paper on your way home?</font>

27
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

28
00:01:17,720 --> 00:01:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom used to do that too.</font>

29
00:01:19,940 --> 00:01:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'd always stand that way when I left.</font>

30
00:01:24,910 --> 00:01:27,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe we got it from our mom.</font>

