<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emiri told me I should.</font>

34
00:01:33,530 --> 00:01:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not that. I meant you 
don't need my permission.</font>

35
00:01:39,090 --> 00:01:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as your school's 
