<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cool. Call me Mori, then.</font>

42
00:01:57,930 --> 00:01:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you decided?</font>

43
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:01,890
