<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not yet.</font>

51
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that I really care...</font>

52
00:02:17,010 --> 00:02:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, same.</font>

53
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder how everyone else decides.</font>

54
00:02:23,490 --> 00:02:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you interested in anything?</font>

55
