71
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good grief. What did you do to your hair?</font>

72
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look like a boy.</font>

73
00:03:12,980 --> 00:03:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so cute!</font>

74
00:03:14,660 --> 00:03:16,530
