<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the only one who likes it.</font>

76
00:03:19,170 --> 00:03:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You mean your parents don't?</font>

77
00:03:21,830 --> 00:03:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess not. I'll have to convince them.</font>

