132
00:06:44,510 --> 00:06:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, my. Welcome, Asa-chan.</font>

133
00:06:48,330 --> 00:06:50,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you been taking care of her?</font>

134
00:06:50,410 --> 00:06:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose.</font>

135
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have some tea. I bought some cake.</font>

136
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:56,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for having me.</font>

137
00:06:57,520 --> 00:07:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go sort through my stuff first.</font>

138
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least sit down for a cup of tea.</font>

139
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That one cup of tea takes forever.</font>

140
00:07:05,850 --> 00:07:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make some myself if I get thirsty.</font>

141
00:07:08,920 --> 00:07:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodness.</font>

142
00:07:09,670 --> 00:07:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a cold one, isn't she?</font>

143
00:07:11,670 --> 00:07:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be like her.</font>

144
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, come on in here.</font>

145
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still reading kid stuff like that?</font>

146
00:07:31,950 --> 00:07:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You used to read it too.</font>

147
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obviously not anymore.</font>

148
