<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine by me!</font>

150
00:07:51,650 --> 00:07:54,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't enjoy all these 
memories rushing back.</font>

151
00:07:58,810 --> 00:08:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't you take a right here?</font>

152
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's definitely a hidden path.</font>

153
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch out! They're coming!</font>

154
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sis, be quiet!</font>

155
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go right! They're gonna get you!</font>

156
