<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Both of you, sit further 
away from the TV!</font>

157
00:08:11,580 --> 00:08:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about college?</font>

158
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you decided?</font>

159
