179
00:09:23,420 --> 00:09:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't hate everyone, you know...</font>

180
00:09:26,690 --> 00:09:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I have to admit...
 she's become dull and snide.</font>

181
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:36,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe it's because we left home, Dad died,</font>

182
00:09:36,660 --> 00:09:39,680
