189
00:10:00,470 --> 00:10:02,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I remember Grandma saying...</font>

190
00:10:02,490 --> 00:10:06,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could you die before your own mother?</font>

191
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:08,280
