193
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you felt that, that's what matters.</font>

194
00:10:17,250 --> 00:10:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what Mom was really like.</font>

195
00:10:22,210 --> 00:10:24,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What she used to think about...</font>

196
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not something you'd know
