274
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that one?</font>

275
00:14:10,570 --> 00:14:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's what I'm thinking.</font>

276
00:14:11,950 --> 00:14:13,490
