288
00:14:33,550 --> 00:14:35,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, who?</font>

289
00:14:35,050 --> 00:14:36,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The short-haired girl.</font>

290
00:14:36,190 --> 00:14:37,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

