<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As guardian, you'll be obligated</font>

344
00:16:39,700 --> 00:16:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to submit income and expenditure 
reports from now on.</font>

345
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry, I haven't been able to...</font>

346
00:16:44,370 --> 00:16:49,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I assumed you were aware of this entry
when you submitted the bankbook to me.</font>

347
00:16:49,990 --> 00:16:51,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or were you not?</font>

348
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:54,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}W-Wait. C-Could you slow down a bit?</font>

349
00:16:56,020 --> 00:16:59,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All this at once is scaring me.</font>

350
00:17:00,250 --> 00:17:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scaring you?</font>

351
00:17:02,430 --> 00:17:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry about that.</font>

352
00:17:04,340 --> 00:17:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't touched this account other than 
for school expenses and her allowance.</font>

353
00:17:09,670 --> 00:17:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All our daily expenses 
come from my account.</font>

354
00:17:12,570 --> 00:17:17,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I've set up an automatic 
transfer for her allowance.</font>

355
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an4}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="16"><font color="#7f7f7f">\hAutomatic
Transfer</font></font></font></font>

356
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an4}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="16"><font color="#7f7f7f">\hAutomatic
Transfer</font></font></font></font>

357
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an4}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="16"><font color="#7f7f7f">Cash</font></font></font></font>

358
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an4}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="16"><font color="#7f7f7f">Deposit</font></font></font></font>

359
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an4}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="16"><font color="#7f7f7f">Deposit</font></font></font></font>

360
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an4}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="16"><font color="#7f7f7f">Cash card</font></font></font></font>

361
00:17:13,670 --> 00:17:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an4}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="16"><font color="#7f7f7f">Asa Takumi</font></font></font></font>

362
00:17:17,330 --> 00:17:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd forget otherwise.</font>

363
00:17:19,370 --> 00:17:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So to address your point...</font>

364
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I didn't notice this when 
I sent a copy of the bankbook.</font>

365
00:17:25,450 --> 00:17:29,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I have no clue what this 
300,000 yen is about...</font>

366
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:32,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me.</font>

367
00:17:32,740 --> 00:17:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did come at you a bit aggressively.</font>

368
00:17:35,620 --> 00:17:41,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so focused on the rights of 
the child that I got too heated.</font>

369
00:17:41,730 --> 00:17:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And since you wouldn't answer my calls,</font>

370
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I took you for the shameless sort.</font>

371
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Impact"><font color="#d5d5d5">The shameless sort</font></font></font>

372
00:17:46,330 --> 00:17:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for being so shameless...</font>

373
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I didn't mean that! I apologize!</font>

374
00:17:52,430 --> 00:17:56,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's fine. I just can't do normal 
things like a normal person.</font>

375
00:17:56,740 --> 00:17:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a computer.</font>

376
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bought a computer. A Mac laptop.</font>

377
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

378
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was this something you needed for school?</font>

379
00:18:05,810 --> 00:18:06,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

380
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did someone tell you to buy it?</font>

381
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

382
00:18:12,660 --> 00:18:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa?</font>

383
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

384
00:18:18,730 --> 00:18:23,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I could make some 
music myself with a laptop.</font>

385
00:18:23,940 --> 00:18:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That you might be against me
 joining the band club.</font>

386
00:18:27,490 --> 00:18:29,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? But I told you...</font>

387
00:18:29,500 --> 00:18:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa-san, has Koudai-san ever 
restricted your actions before?</font>

388
00:18:35,450 --> 00:18:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

389
00:18:36,710 --> 00:18:40,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How you feel is no one's 
business but yours.</font>

390
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one has the right 
to shame you for it.</font>

391
00:18:44,770 --> 00:18:45,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what.</font>

392
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never. Not in the slightest.</font>

393
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she's an adult, so...</font>

394
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:54,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought she might say no.</font>

395
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="36"><font face="Arial"><font color="#58513c">...was her own fault.</font></font></font></font>

396
00:18:54,690 --> 00:18:56,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be whoever you want to be.</font>

397
00:18:56,460 --> 00:18:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#58513c"><b>___________________________</b></font></font>

398
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#58513c"><b>___________________________</b></font></font>

399
00:18:57,490 --> 00:19:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just felt... so confused...</font>

400
00:18:57,630 --> 00:18:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#58513c"><b>___________________________</b></font></font>

401
00:18:57,970 --> 00:18:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#58513c"><b>___________________________</b></font></font>

402
00:18:58,400 --> 00:19:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14">{\an8}<font color="#5b5646">Eel</font></font></font></font>

403
00:19:02,170 --> 00:19:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry...</font>

404
00:19:04,850 --> 00:19:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa, we should talk about this,
 but some other time.</font>

405
00:19:09,650 --> 00:19:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not go rinse your face?</font>

406
00:19:17,620 --> 00:19:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told her she could join 
the band club if she wanted.</font>

407
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:25,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she said her parents 
wouldn't like it.</font>

408
00:19:26,190 --> 00:19:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She seems to be in the 
midst of finding herself.</font>

409
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:33,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understandable for her age, 
even barring the circumstances.</font>

410
00:19:36,090 --> 00:19:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you ever need to talk to someone
not Koudai-san or a teacher,</font>

411
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">please feel free reach out.</font>

412
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay.</font>

413
00:19:42,370 --> 00:19:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there's anything I can do,
 let me know.</font>

414
00:19:44,930 --> 00:19:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have much experience,</font>

415
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:51,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so this is my first time 
meeting someone like you.</font>

416
00:19:51,620 --> 00:20:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Impact"><font color="#d5d5d5">Someone like me</font></font></font>

417
00:19:51,820 --> 00:19:54,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone like me...</font>

418
00:19:54,380 --> 00:19:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, I'm sorry! I just meant your job!</font>

419
00:19:57,040 --> 00:20:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Impact"><font color="#d5d5d5">Doesn't answer calls</font></font></font>

420
00:19:57,040 --> 00:20:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<font face="Impact"><font color="#d5d5d5">Barely makes deadlines</font></font></font>

421
00:19:57,760 --> 00:20:02,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone who doesn't answer calls 
and barely makes deadlines...</font>

422
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm here to support you
and your life together!</font>

423
00:20:04,970 --> 00:20:06,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, please...</font>

424
00:20:07,630 --> 00:20:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Allow me to help from now on.</font>

425
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, thank you.</font>

426
00:20:19,030 --> 00:20:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi, Kasamachi-kun. Come on in.</font>

427
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey... I brought some oysters.</font>

428
00:20:24,370 --> 00:20:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

429
00:20:25,850 --> 00:20:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Tono, an attorney.</font>

430
00:20:28,210 --> 00:20:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you happen to be Koudai-san's 
significant other?</font>

431
00:20:33,080 --> 00:20:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="8">{\an8}<font color="#5b5646">Eel</font></font></font></font>

432
00:20:33,080 --> 00:20:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="10">{\an8}<font color="#5b5646">I have to return the laptop</font></font></font></font>

433
00:20:33,850 --> 00:20:35,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Mac, huh?</font>

434
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:38,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll buy it, if you want.</font>

435
00:20:38,090 --> 00:20:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That would just make 
things more complicated.</font>

436
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

437
00:20:44,110 --> 00:20:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But man, an attorney?</font>

438
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tired?</font>

439
00:20:50,070 --> 00:20:53,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah... You could say that.</font>

440
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just pretend you're getting 
hugged by a big dog.</font>

441
00:21:00,260 --> 00:21:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Bernese Mountain Dog.</font>

442
00:21:01,860 --> 00:21:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That</i> big?</font>

443
00:21:03,670 --> 00:21:07,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This reminds me, I did the same 
thing to Asa the other day.</font>

444
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must have picked it up from you.</font>

445
00:21:13,630 --> 00:21:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think Asa likes this song.</font>

446
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She sings it sometimes.</font>

447
00:21:17,970 --> 00:21:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa!</font>

448
00:21:19,380 --> 00:21:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa-san!</font>

449
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's that group you like. They're on TV.</font>

450
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna watch? Come on over.</font>

451
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:34,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're squished.</font>

452
00:21:34,620 --> 00:21:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You like this stuff?</font>

453
00:21:35,810 --> 00:21:39,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I like this song's bass line.</font>

454
00:21:39,950 --> 00:21:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good taste. You have a fine ear.</font>

455
00:21:42,890 --> 00:21:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

456
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-chan...</font>

457
00:21:48,840 --> 00:21:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I join the band club?</font>

458
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. Do what you want to do.</font>

459
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I will.</font>

460
00:22:00,770 --> 00:22:03,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right here! This bass line!</font>

461
00:22:04,570 --> 00:22:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty cool.</font>

